    "body": "### Problem\n\nWhen using vim.pack.add it's more difficult to use plugins that have dependencies, and if it failed to install those deps then appropriate action to be taken.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n`vim.pack.add({\n\t{\n        src=\"git@github.com:nvim-telescope/telescope.nvim.git\",\n        name=\"telescope\",\n        deps=\"https://github.com/nvim-lua/plenary.nvim.git\"\n        }\n})`\n",
